      "content": "Fiona’s daily news, &amp;.23<br><i class=\"emoji\"><b>1⃣️</b></i>重大消息<br>1-ETH ETF通过并将开始正式交易<br>2-随着选举进入未知领域，拜登的退出刺激 Polymarket 日交易量创纪录的 2800 万美元，对美国总统选举获胜者的赌注飙升至超过 3 亿美元<br><br><i class=\"emoji\"><b>2⃣️</b></i>公司：<br>1-传英伟达将推出中国特供版「Blackwell」架构 B20 加速器<br>2-马斯克：特斯拉有望 2026 年大规模生产人形机器人，供其他公司使用<br>3- 微软技术故障造成全球损失或超 10 亿美元<br><br><i class=\"emoji\"><b>3⃣️</b></i>行情预测<br>1-有分析师指出：在特朗普参加比特币大会之前获利了结将会付出昂贵的代价。<a href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2024/07/22/taking-profits-on-bitcoin-ahead-of-trump-conference-appearance-could-be-expensive-exercise-analyst/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2024/07/22/taking-profits-on-bitcoin-ahead-of-trump-conference-appearance-could-be-expensive-exercise-analyst/\">https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2024/07/22/taking-profits-on-bitcoin-ahead-of-trump-conference-appearance-could-be-expensive-exercise-analyst/</a><br>2-10x Research 创始人Markus Thielen预计特朗普将赢得 11 月大选，引发 SEC 主席Gary Gensler 提前退位。（放鞭炮庆祝）<a class=\"tgme_widget_message_link_preview\" href=\"https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2024/07/22/taking-profits-on-bitcoin-ahead-of-trump-conference-appearance-could-be-expensive-exercise-analyst\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Traders could be forgiven for wanting to cash in after bitcoin's {{BTC}} quick rise of more than 20% to the current $67,000 from its early July lows, but another possibly major positive catalyst might be just days away, said 10x Research founder Markus Thielen.\">\n  \n  <div class=\"link_preview_site_name accent_color\" dir=\"auto\">Coindesk</div>\n  <img class=\"link_preview_image\" alt=\"Taking Profits on Bitcoin Ahead of Trump Conference Appearance Could Be 'Expensive Exercise': Analyst\" src=\"/static/9c11773d64a0f33acba18accbb08b101.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  <div class=\"link_preview_title\" dir=\"auto\">Taking Profits on Bitcoin Ahead of Trump Conference Appearance Could Be 'Expensive Exercise': Analyst</div>\n  <div class=\"link_preview_d